Class DefaultElevator

  • java.lang.Object
    • cw3.DefaultElevator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Elevator

    public class DefaultElevator
extends java.lang.Object
implements Elevator
    Elevator object containing the default algorithm

    Start at the bottom floor, then go up each floor one and a time to the top. Then come back down one floor at a time again

    Author:
    pete
